g":"你班友都傻下傻下<br />\n唔係買左個單位邊個會洗咁多錢裝修間公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608f39700cb6925b149d5b86be464b21894db114","tid":40042,"uid":66040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"究竟要有幾多雜物 先用得哂咁多個櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf6daa9ec4ca210cb7175b94e2c22e6967cb3fc","tid":40042,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"拉登仔係咪覺得住公屋就唔可以靚裝修，要住到成隻狗咁先有資格繼續住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f65df0d4fecc0bde50d5c2115b645ee7112c641","tid":40042,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟要有幾多雜物 先用得哂咁多個櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公屋妹係咁，因為住慣地方細，成日唔夠位用，所以一裝修就要整好多櫃。有錢人就無呢個問題，會好識享受，會整好多唔實用但好靚ge野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f739089f188da7b2f5e3db645bcfc7a864867513","tid":40042,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉登仔係咪覺得住公屋就唔可以靚裝修，要住到成隻狗咁先有資格繼續住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港依家居住舒適度係<br />\n獨立屋&gt;黃金地段豪宅&gt;居屋&gt;公屋&gt;偽豪宅"},{"pid":"88b3429d8ff0b6e1fea1e1bb4f145a472dfebb6d","tid":40042,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟要有幾多雜物 先用得哂咁多個櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公屋妹係咁，因為住慣地方細，成日唔夠位用，所以一裝修就要整好多櫃。有錢人就無呢個問題，會好識享受，會整好多唔實用但好靚ge野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢人間屋千幾二千呎，淨係衣帽間都等於公屋個廳啦。放曬雜物入去咪唔覺個廳多野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}